{"tid":599950,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係好憎陸運會嘅lunch time","createTime":"2018-03-21T02:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T02:17:31.000Z","uid":34489,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f116f98fdf1d07ef67f26a5a54ce08479764a538","tid":599950,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T02:04:49.000Z","msg":"就快就陸運會 仲記得上年陸運會lunch time果陣 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n大家一堆堆朋友咁出去搵餐廳食飯 我就一個人行黎行去禁手機又要扮等緊朋友黎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n之後仲要好辛苦咁搵間冇乜同校學生去既餐廳食飯 因為好怕比人見到自己一個係到食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n上年我就專登坐taxi坐左10分鐘左右 離個會場都有一後距離 諗住唔會撞到人 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n點知入到間餐廳 就撞正成堆老師 連埋我2個班主任都係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n其中一個班主任就問:咦 你黎到咁遠食既? 我地都係渣車黎炸喎 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n我: 係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上網check過喱間出名啊麻 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n佢:係咩? 我未聽過喎 我地都係是但揀 近會場果邊滿哂人啊 冇計啦..係呢 你一個人? <br />\r\n<br />\r\n我:唔係..我朋友黎緊..(當然係老吹架啦) <br />\r\n<br />\r\n之後我就即刻打比我個best friend叫佢坐taxi黎 我話請埋佢車錢同飯錢 但佢都唔肯 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n我唯有趁班老師傾緊計果陣就叫左個外賣坐車番會場到食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n第2日陸運會我連番都冇番tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗番起真係好慘...點解上天要咁對毒撚...唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd56c0a86fa6fc41b715060c26294e82f9100f42","tid":599950,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T02:08:37.000Z","msg":"留名睇新會然"},{"pid":"ef1be758b437f31ac5eb71e53e64a79f4f9dab33","tid":599950,"uid":78473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T02:10:55.000Z","msg":"學術台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c49c6a5a5fded96396cb29277381a3a35e089d","tid":599950,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T02:14:07.000Z","msg":"已射thx"},{"pid":"832de50c116428b451e2ae7d1a9500bea8ded6f1","tid":599950,"uid":125733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06c49c6a5a5fded96396cb29277381a3a35e089d","tid":599950,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T02:14:07.000Z","msg":"已射thx"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T02:15:01.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"e37b282ab8c3aa7b7a558291fcc805be4d5984a0","tid":599950,"uid":76098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T02:15:48.000Z","msg":"有best fd仲扮毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f0465883176870b6ded417abc7ffa8719fb7b0","tid":599950,"uid":38737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T02:17:31.000Z","msg":"呢篇潮文好耐先見一次"}]}